description: Screenshots: http://www.imagesum.com/2018/09/image-1_58.html Info: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/70th_Primetime_Emmy_Awards Resolution: 960x540 Format: .mp4 Audio: AAC English Date: September 17, 2018 (Ceremony) Location: Microsoft Theater, Los Angeles, California Presented by: Academy of Television Arts & Sciences Hosted by: Michael Che Colin Jost The 70th Primetime Emmy Awards honored the best in U.S. prime time television programming from June 1, 2017 until May 31, 2018, as chosen by the Academy of Television Arts & Sciences. The ceremony was held live on September 17, 2018, at the Microsoft Theater in Downtown Los Angeles, California, and was broadcast in the U.S. by NBC. The ceremony was hosted by Michael Che and Colin Jost
